###########
Instroduction:
###########
A post-processing code can calculate normalized trace of interatomic force 
constant tensors versus atomic distances from FORCE_CONSTANTS produced by phonopy.

###########
References:
###########
1. Nat. Commun., 2014, 5, 3525.
2. J. Materiomics, 2020, 6, 723-728.
3. Phys. Chem. Chem. Phys., 2020, 22, 18556-18561.

###########
Useage:
###########
1. Chmod +x trace_ifc.x
2. Phonon calculations with phonopy.
3. ./trace_ifc.x (It reads FORCE_CONSTANTS and SPOSCAR produced by phonopy.)
4. Plot trace_ifc.dat with origin.

###########
Format of trace_ifc.dat
###########
       # 1bond, trace_ifc, 2bond, trace_ifc, 3bond, trace_ifc, 4bond, trace_ifc......
 1atom
 2atom
 3atom
 ......


If you have further problems or want to report a bug, please feel free to contanct me:
